caption.text:
Do you know that every hour, a woman in Indonesia died because of cervical cancer? It accounts for 34% of all cancers that attack women. It has a slow progress but it won't show any signs until it gets to cancer. How do you prevent it? Use HPV vaccine! It is effective until 70% to prevent cervical cancer. You can also do an early detection with IVA or Pap Smear in your nearest Puskesmas.

I am now aware of cervical cancer and I'm spreading the awareness to you!

This campaign is a part of @LigaMedika FKUI, wait for our event on March 12th, 2016.
